            <title>[CASSANDRA-5814] RowIndexEntry.deletionTime raises UnsupportedOperationException when upgrading to 1.2.7</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5814</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Upgrading from 1.2.5 to 1.2.7 immediately caused the following exception. We stopped the node and reverted to 1.2.5.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll note that we also run a 1.2.6 cluster that is doing fine, so I think this is caused by a change in 1.2.7.&lt;/p&gt;

